Vinay Suri

I have compiled these on a linux machine running Ubuntu.

For Reference, to compile:
gcc -o <file> <file>.c -lglut -lGLU -lGL -lm -lGL

Make sure Grass.bmp and sky.bmp are in the same directory as sports.c
 
 Controls:
 - To move person 1: ^-w <-a v-s >-d
 - To move the ball: ^-i <-j v-k >-l
 - Record functions:
	z - Start
	x - Stop
	c - Load
	v - Reset
	b - Playback
	n - Save
 - To toggle on/off syncronize: m
